=== Glass Unit ===
id: frontend.calendar
version: 0.1.0
language: typescript

=== Intent ===
purpose: Interactive month calendar component that highlights days with journal entries and supports date selection for filtering the dashboard timeline.
source:
  kind: prd
  reference: "PRD Section 9.1 â€” Dashboard Calendar"
parent: frontend.dashboard
stakeholder: user
subIntents: []
approvalStatus: approved

=== Contract ===
requires:
  - "Set of entry date strings (YYYY-MM-DD format)"
  - "Optional selected date and onSelect callback"
guarantees:
  on_success:
    - "Renders month grid with Sun-Sat column headers"
    - "Previous/next month navigation buttons"
    - "Days with entries marked with blue dot indicator"
    - "Click date to select (filters dashboard), click again to deselect"
    - "Previous/next month dates shown in muted color"
  on_failure:
    - "Empty entryDates set renders calendar with no highlights"
invariants:
  - "Calendar always shows complete weeks (padding from adjacent months)"
  - "Selection is toggle-based (click selected date to clear)"
fails:
  RenderError: "Invalid date input handled gracefully"
